      <strong>Mountain (yama)</strong>
      <p style="margin:0.4rem 0 0; font-size:0.9rem;">Three peaks sticking up from the ground — the tallest peak in the center, smaller ones on each side. Picture Mt. Fuji.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius:0.5rem; padding:1rem;">
      <div style="font-size:2.5rem; text-align:center; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">木</div>
      <strong>Tree (ki)</strong>
      <p style="margin:0.4rem 0 0; font-size:0.9rem;">A trunk going up, branches spreading left and right at the top, roots spreading left and right at the bottom. A perfect stylized tree.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius:0.5rem; padding:1rem;">
